 It was also in this camp where we spent our Xmas consid the circ we had a veri decent time . Box morn the 26th was detail in charg of a fatigu parti went up to Wytschaet villag on road make . Next day I went with an offic N.C.Os had a good look round the Front line , Support reserv trench which was to be our home for a few day . On the 30th I came a big thud for I was detail as platoon advanc guard had to go to the front line have a look at platoon sector also went out on patrol next morn came back to Wytschaet villag made a big fire thaw myself . I met my platoon that same night guid them into the front line took over . Our posit here was on the outpost scheme with piquet line , support , reserv etc no movement whatev could be made whatev . On the night of the 1st Januari I was detail in charg of wire parti in no man land did a few hour work . Next night the 2nd we chang over we move back to support where we had to do fatigu etc we last there for three day . We again move chang over with the front line on the night of the 5th .
